Make VIP tangibly better: faster kart, accessible lounge, live trophy room

- KartService: normal kart is now plain & average (speed 52); VIP Turbo
  Kart is much faster (speed 140) and flashier so VIP clearly pays off.
- PlotService upper tier: support cores moved to the back corners so they
  no longer block the staircase (the lounge was unreachable). Wider stairs
  land flush on the deck. VIP Lounge is OPEN and advertises its perks to
  everyone (perk list + "Get VIP in the Shop" CTA) instead of hiding them.
- Trophy Room now has a live display board (tagged TrophyDisplay) showing
  cup stage, matches won, rebirths and your best card.
- New TrophyController (client) fills that board from the profile; wired
  into ClientMain's boot + ProfileUpdated handler.

